":101294,"uid":7365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇睇個個補番post</blockquote><br />\n見解唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得部分唔夠詳細 吸引唔到我睇<br />\nglasslip<del>同迷家</del>介紹下<br />\n未睇過想開</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e891cd0088fa2916dc31ef08c517202357410ed7","tid":101294,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:12:57.000Z","msg":"一次講問我咁多套有啲難答喎清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n魔法戰爭係魔法壙世巨著, 可比魔戒, 伏筆同展開環環扣緊, 真係要自己睇先領會到佢有幾神, 細佬我筆墨所限描述唔到, 唯一可以講既係佢結尾留白左, 等觀眾可以心領神會, 真係好出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nglasslip表面上係將意識流融入青春群像劇既劃時代巨著, 但係更深層次係探討緊平行世界同命運, 裡面講既玻璃碎片就係世界既可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n迷家就係透過懸疑既都市傳說納鳴村探討榮格心理學, 納鳴現象可以話係Libido既具現化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至高指令以超能力戰鬥為主題, 出色在每一話都好似唔連貫咁超展開, 我都唔想劇透咁多, 始終爆點呢家野要自己去享受, 最多可以講既係幕後大黑手不停咁換, 集集新鮮集集爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4268d0ee764f2364a0bb2f760fac34b863f66766","tid":101294,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:14:14.000Z","msg":"樓上好波"},{"pid":"3bacd60ffe85e72a89e71885c3ecc05df7893c2b","tid":101294,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a07fac3581112ef06867da9cd82bd46f6aa45e7","tid":101294,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"不過光宗清應該熟迷家多過我, 希望細佬有咩理解錯, 清唔好屌鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce73b3ab7ed48d7af6b63c0d258b88d13ccc95b","tid":101294,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:19:39.000Z","msg":"終於有同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla